[ LOW(fx_finish_dummy) ][ HIGH(PIE) ]
After overwrite:
[ LOW(win)             ][ HIGH(PIE) ]
We only change:
bytes 0..3
and leave:
bytes 4..7 (HIGH) untouched

Result
fx_finish_dummy  →  win
Even though we never performed a full 8-byte write.





